data.description: JUST REDUCED $10K!!! Welcome Home!! 4Br 2.5 Bath Home is awaiting new owners. Front entry opens to the kitchen and Great Room. Stainless Steel Refrigerator and Dishwasher 2023; Premium wood laminate flooring front entry, the kitcjen and downstairs bath. carpet in great room, dining room and living room (used as office). Primary BR Dbl Closet and walkin (Built in Shelves), Single Closet, Double vanity, Garden Tub and Separate Shower. Crack in Primary Bath Sink (no leaks). Exhaust fan in primary bath (2023); Downstairs ceiling fans, hall lights, and upstairs hall lights will be replaced by 10/21/2023. Both Kitchen and Great room doors open to the screened in porch (14 X 11.5) which connects to the patio. The backyard has Wood Burning Brick firepit and playground equipment. Home Sold "As Is" - Price reflects need for painting. No Repairs or Concessions Paid by Seller.
